/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />荒謬判刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉<span class=\"gold\">伸腳絆倒</span>警員 前公務員襲警罪成判<span class=\"gold\">囚兩月</span> 官：以儆效尤、防範未然<br />\n<br />\n涉向便衣警<span class=\"gold\">背脊貼文宣</span> 地產經紀襲警罪成<span class=\"gold\">囚 3 周</span> 官：行為極具羞辱成份<br />\n<br />\n中大內地生畢業禮涉<span class=\"gold\">持刀</span>唱國歌 獲撤控准簽保守行為 官質疑：嚴重過雷射筆<br />\n<br />\n【11.11 三罷】教師被控襲警罪成 一度遭還押小欖 判<span class=\"gold\">囚 9 周</span>准保釋候上訴 官斥未見悔意<br />\n<br />\n陳志全私人檢控郭偉強 律政司<span class=\"gold\">要求介入</span> <span class=\"gold\">不提證供起訴</span><br />\n<br />\n屯門山景邨麥當勞打人案 施襲男子被<span class=\"gold\">判社服令</span><br />\n打人+刑事毁壞唔洗坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【旺角 10.6 】內地客、清路障男子遭「私了」 清潔工判囚 4 年 另兩被告各囚 15 個月<br />\n第二被告開遮 推咗一下 坐15個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地盤工暴動襲痱滋警罪成<span class=\"gold\">囚4年</span> 官：判刑不考慮政治 對再判品格良好青年入獄感無奈<br />\n圍狗總案 事發歷時15秒 好似都係打咗幾鎚踢幾腳 咁就4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同下面斬人睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連儂隧道斬人導遊求情：不幸事因社運 <span class=\"gold\">官讚情操高尚</span> <span class=\"gold\">同情減刑</span>囚 45 月 狂轟示威者<br />\n拎把刀落街明顯有預謀 斬到人入icu都係坐得嗰4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉亮𠝹刀疑襲警遭女警槍擊 無業漢被控轉介區院再訊<br />\n𠝹刀就開槍 唔講以為俾西瓜刀劈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />荒謬判刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n節錄唔曬靠巴絲幫我加上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8f7a1a41da809cf6a6d953de524e095b42a7fc","tid":2291654,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:12:48.000Z","msg":"成日有班on9日日就法治已死OMDB<br />\n係人都知一早死鳩左+OMDB真係好on9啦<br />\n咁但係日日鞭屍有撚用咩<br />\n有利判決：文宣正苦+黑狗做嘅唔合法<br />\n紅到黑反常理嘅判決：文宣法官唔公平公正<br />\n雙重標準識唔識呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc4bf8f5f28960fdc21b31cc79c073d9de09052","tid":2291654,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:13:21.000Z","msg":"咪係，你真係夠膽當面叫毅進show證先算啦，到時佢咪又係打你一身然後屈你襲警拘捕阻差辦公然後國安法拉你再話你港獨份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c491f4fbdfd8c19885a8fb36dc7480a167c9efc","tid":2291654,"uid":65027,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e2404aa8f6635c0f75ed20d25ef9ab72736d6116","tid":2291654,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6727693738f2f1cfc1ac1077bb88a9e56ff700d2","tid":2291654,"uid":65027,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"cls <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留言開心下都要屌老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:10:35.000Z","msg":"咁多義士入獄，仲開心到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:15:24.000